</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph id="8BA1AF6D7607FFC169931C16178BFC80" blockId="8.[151,1437,779,1426]" box="[198,1430,779,805]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Female. Nearly identical to male. Eyes separated by twice width of ocellar triangle. Scales on front paler.</paragraph>
